		<div class="layout-item-intro">
			<h2>Related Selections</h2>
			<ul class="list-inline list-inline-tight"><li><a href="/topics/counterculture" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Counterculture</a></li><li><a href="/topics/sustainable-living" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Sustainable Living</a></li><li><a href="/topics/physical-health" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Physical Health</a></li><li><a href="/topics/spirituality" class="xsmall link-alt link-text">Spirituality</a></li></ul>		</div>

		<div class="articles-l2">
							


<article class="block-content block-content-l5 block-content-reversed">
		

	<div class="block-content-header">
							<h6 class="b-content-section heading-square heading-border"><a href="/sections/essays-memoirs-true-stories">Essays, Memoirs, and True Stories</a></h6>
		

